{"tid":498813,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"網售自製遊戲機預載千款侵權遊戲　海關拘2人","createTime":"2017-12-14T06:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T11:18:08.000Z","uid":42675,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3eb3ad2a727cda49f91c2e1ca1b1c943e06078","tid":498813,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/145607_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F145607_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5a5d132d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/145620_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F145620_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=36aae514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「將機鋪搬返屋企」、「支援遊戲超過7,000款」，一間智能產品公司今年中推出一款自家品牌家用遊戲機，標榜僅約3吋機身載有逾7,000款懷舊遊戲，包括街機、Game Gear、Game Boy、紅白機等，可直插電視或平板電腦使用，又支援多人對戰。該公司拍攝宣傳片在facebook推銷，連手掣的遊戲機套裝售價949港元，聲稱全球限量1,000部。 <br />\n<br />\n該公司為吸引顧客，更提供免費送貨、原廠保養等服務，吸引不少資深玩家購買。惟海關近日接獲舉報，指該款電視遊戲機預載的遊戲懷疑侵犯版權，遂於今日下午採取反盜版執法行動，掩至深水埗福仁商場門市作突擊搜查，起出12部遊戲機套裝，總值約1.1萬港元，將男店主（35歲）及男店員（23歲）拘捕，涉嫌涉及銷售或為售賣用途而管有侵權物品，2人被海關押走調查。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/145628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F145628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1bd27918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/145632_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F145632_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9ccd46f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次是海關首次緝破有店舖以自製遊戲機預載侵權遊戲的案件，初步相信該公司運作約1年，半年前起出售該款侵權產品，遊戲機由內地廠商製造，行動仍然繼續，不排除有更多人被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，該公司總部設於葵興一棟工廈，過往曾推出多款創意智能產品，包括具攝錄功能的遙控「偵探車」、供小朋友學寫字的手寫板、無線投影「手指」、GPS追踪手錶等，其中手錶具備單向監聽、一鍵求救、運動量記錄等功能，吸引不少家長訂購，用於遙距監控子女及防止走失。 <br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/mobile/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001.html&d=y%2Fqd8MyStx9%2BQdFqO2ApWp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d63c1cbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/mobile/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n之前賣&quot;紀念版gameboy&quot;嗰班人點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df64ccd03b2e4e48880bb667b4668d31f975e5b","tid":498813,"uid":18333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"Restart workshop,?"},{"pid":"f8dcdb52c8808c75e9dc9e50169bc363be8b4cf5","tid":498813,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"raspberry pi + retropie<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40d9234cad2686918774d42d26c686b769ef8a1","tid":498813,"uid":31927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"紀念版gameboy<br />\n係咪有巴打開箱直接丟落垃圾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fcac2380139b2442cc75ca74183de626058c84","tid":498813,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紀念版gameboy<br />\n係咪有巴打開箱直接丟落垃圾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀"},{"pid":"2e5dbbe3b6d183dd9b71a2ec65cd910997a86ec7","tid":498813,"uid":9887,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"啲月光寶盒，老翻迷你紅白機又唔拉？"},{"pid":"1f5abada2c850cc61e40c8921f1f9ae14f590049","tid":498813,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dis