e":"2017-12-14T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/334649/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/334649/page/1</a><br />\n部野仲出左兩代<br />\n第一代伏到連內置遊戲都冇<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">不過可能係咁海關反而冇拉到</span></span>"},{"pid":"ee2dd894954b80e834f17f38cef7948859d4844a","tid":498813,"uid":59435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}